	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Okay, this is a really really dumb unprofessional newbie question, but anyway, I took apart a cart that I was going to use as a devcart, and I looked in it, and it didn't even have chips! it had these blobs of black stuff! I'm sorry, I should probably know this, but what are those? and also, the cart  thing that you insert into the NES itself had a gap in the middle that had no pins. All carts that I've taken apart that had chips in it had all pins on that. When it has a gap, does that signify that it has blobs, and not chips?

		

		</td>
